                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">\n                    <add>Yiddish</add>\n                </hi>\n            </p>\n            <p>May God seek the peace of the man<lb/> of his covenant I extend to him my<lb/>\n                covenant of peace. My friend, who is like a<lb/> brother to me. The “Zaddick” of\n                clean hands<lb/> and a pure heart, the all-embracing wise<lb/> man, our teacher\n                    <persName>Rabbi Isaac Leeser</persName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Honored Friend:</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I have prevailed upon the trustees<lb/> that it is time to send you\n                money. No one<lb/> had anything against it, but before they<lb/> would pay, the\n                people wanted to be urged on the<lb/> matter, and I did not like to urge them\n                for<lb/> they might suppose I made a profit from this<lb/> business, since the book\n                cost them so very much.<lb/> I should therefore very much appreciate<lb/> your\n                sending immediately a letter<lb/> to the treasurers, <persName>Moses\n                    Bronner</persName>, of the firm of<lb/>\n                <persName>Bronner and Seburg<add>?</add></persName>, and at the same time<lb/> to me\n                in which you earnestly demand<lb/> money. In view of the fact that I had\n                pro-<lb/>mised to send you the money the first<lb/> of this month. I am convinced\n                that you will<lb/> then receive the money by return mail.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I want to inform you that the<lb/> organization called Harmonia,\n                consisting<lb/> of 18 of the most intelligent Jews of this<lb/> town, which was\n                organized only two<lb/> months ago, sent a very handsome <date>Purim</date><lb/>\n                gift to <persName role=\"author\">Dr. Illoway</persName>, namely a very pretty</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3t727z3h/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
